Prometheus is a powerful open-source metrics collection and alerting system.
It was built for dynamic environments like Kubernetes.
Key features:
 â€¢ Pull-based metrics collection over HTTP (/metrics endpoint)
 â€¢ Time-series database built in
 â€¢ Service discovery (automatically finds pods and services)
 â€¢ Powerful PromQL query language
 â€¢ Alertmanager integration for email, Slack, PagerDuty alerts

In Kubernetes, it scrapes data from:
 â€¢ Node exporters (CPU, memory, disk)
 â€¢ Kubelet, API server, scheduler
 â€¢ Application pods exposing custom metrics
 â€¢ Exporters (e.g., for MySQL, Redis)

